               <title>OXYGEN COMPRESSED LABEL</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>OXYGEN COMPRESSED U.S.P. UN 1072 OXYGEN-2 PRODUCED BY AIR LIQUEFACTION</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>LOT NO ______ EXP DATE________ LITERS______ PRESSURE ______(PSIG AT 70F)</paragraph>
